## Documentation
When making code changes, update related documentation as needed.

## Prompt.AI
The `prompt.ai` folder stores development history and release notes.

After each meaningful task:
- Add an entry to `prompt.ai/development_log.md`
- Include what changed, why, and any follow-up items
- For releases, create `prompt.ai/vX.Y.Z_release_summary.md`
